<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/22003898">疼的时候，呻吟解决什么问题？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="982469" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">如牙疼等，不要想歪了。</div>


